{"tid":1298478,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（轉貼）買島嶼被屈係呃錢，呃巴打入Tg，要報警，搞到完全冇人入Tg。","createTime":"2019-07-09T01:45:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T13:52:14.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"07626c404713fd099022c63ad2905c5b05734442","tid":1298478,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:45:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=7081328&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D7081328%26page%3D1&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0ds83aCWJNbCOh4I0%2FkJBrkU%3D&h=b321eb63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=7081328&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\n六年前，本人已經連續三年一直係高登/膠登開POST討論買島嶼/人工島<br />\r\n<br />\r\n但班「偽獨五毛」走來反對，本人提倡眾籌買島嶼/人工島，更不斷騷擾，妨礙正常討論<br />\r\n<br />\r\n現在班「偽獨五毛」又走出來開POST話買島/建人工島 要眾籌10億，但見本人開POST，佢地不斷話呃錢，<br />\r\n<br />\r\n有巴打講佢地既&rdquo;方舟計畫&rdquo;係營造到一個即將成事嘅格局cap水，根本十劃都無一撇<br />\r\n<br />\r\n話佢地係呃錢陷阱，佢地話本人呃巴打入tg，要報警，搞到完全冇人入黎，手法相當之卑鄙，完全係中共作風。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/09/SisaZj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F09%2FSisaZj.png&h=528902c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29348c398f13b32c6836a45d62aad5ee4d79007e","tid":1298478,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:46:24.000Z","msg":"其實唔洗攪咁多<br />\n去南美買塊氣候相近既地皮咪得<br />\n大陸都四維買殖民地<br />\n好多都大塊過深圳<br />\n<br />\n英國係南美有塊大香港30倍既荒地得幾萬人口"},{"pid":"72c64a219ac1d816b97f01ea38e8d0cd985594ca","tid":1298478,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:49:47.000Z","msg":"共產黨招數一向係人地做乜佢地又跟住做<br />\r\n仲要隨時搶先做<br />\r\n攪到好難分到邊d係騙子<br />\r\n一個人分到都冇用，要全部人都分到好困難<br />\r\n必須進行全民反間諜教育<br />\r\n但港人政治智慧有排都未夠能力學反間諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n可能等老果批死晒會好少少"},{"pid":"340afedd6318e0298afce36353d7360835cf399a","tid":1298478,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:16:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546b75f569b2ca692ea157cf6ab212b88839c4fb","tid":1298478,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:22:33.000Z","msg":"10億 袋袋平安 潛水走人<br />\n<br />\n你估買島買地就可以建國？<br />\n<br />\n到時糧食 交通 工作 政府運作 點解決<br />\n<br />\n最後變死島死地 咪又返香港做奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a93ef088c24a8068f2c2f510175f75696b53c9","tid":1298478,"uid":30561,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:17:14.000Z","msg":"本人提議啲錢係比美國同美國大學，係要西方政府公開話幫香港人建人工島先比錢，好似太平洋國而家找美國建人工島，因美國會承認佢地。 <br />\n<br />\n只要有足夠嘅會員之後，唔會集資，一定係找人去美國傾，如果美國肯幫我地的話，人工島好快就有主權。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n太平洋國而家找美國，因美國嘅技術好犀利，只需要三四年嘅時間就能夠建造一個先進嘅人工島， <br />\n連太平洋國家都能夠畀得起錢，只要二百萬嘅香港人每人出少少錢就已經可以擁有一個屬於香港人嘅地方。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n首個漂浮國家2022年太平洋建成 自設貨幣 <br />\n塔希提島「海上漂浮城市」明年開工 距離海岸約1千米；將發行可在島上消費的加密貨幣「Varyon」；計劃2022年完工 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/news/j4qvzgy.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fnews%2Fj4qvzgy.html&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0ds83aCWJNbCOh4I0%2FkJBrkU%3D&h=31818cbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/news/j4qvzgy.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qFBxhS-psww&amp;list=PLgzNbTFBaN7tK1ZUsifYgII64QX5oDN1D&amp;index=40\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqFBxhS-psww%26list%3DPLgzNbTFBaN7tK1ZUsifYgII64QX5oDN1D%26index%3D40&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0ds83aCWJNbCOh4I0%2FkJBrkU%3D&h=0e555afe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qFBxhS-psww&amp;list=PLgzNbTFBaN7tK1ZUsifYgII64QX5oDN1D&amp;index=40</a><br />\n<br />\n引用的文獻:蒙特維多國家權利義務公約（ <br />\nMontevideo Convention on the Rights and Duties of States）。 <br />\n此公約的第一條款說：在國際法上，一個國家應有以下資格： <br />\n1. 固定的人口（a permanent population）。 <br />\n2. 界限清楚的領土（a defined territory）。 <br />\n3. 政府（government）。 <br />\n4. 與其他國家有建立關係的能力（capacity to enter into relations with the other states）。<br />\n<br />\n所以一定要有美國嘅承認<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家睇班「偽獨五毛」，不斷騷擾，妨礙正常討論 ：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1291865/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1291865/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1292274/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1292274/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"1f327e223e295ce426c8d32e49aceda646e0a1a4","tid":1298478,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff34686918c77403372763db07e4b5e9517ddf6","tid":1298478,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef097bafc5dda7eb2bc6d3f9cb702eef617b3231","tid":1298478,"uid":30561,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"29348c398f13b32c6836a45d62aad5ee4d79007e","tid":1298478,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:46:24.000Z","msg":"其實唔洗攪咁多<br />\n去南美買塊氣候相近既地皮咪得<br />\n大陸都四維買殖民地<br />\n好多都大塊過深圳<br />\n<br />\n英國係南美有塊大香港30倍既荒地得幾萬人口"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:22:50.000Z","msg":"佢地要有主權  之後 方舟要有軍隊！<br />\n<br />\n所以要搞人工島。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/09/24eF1t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F09%2F24eF1t.png&h=7ffd70b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢哋話要先爭取居留權，以&quot;公司&quot;自立-&gt; 2）自治權 -&gt; 3）最後主權 -》之後方舟要有軍隊<br />\n<br />\n那有一個國家可以比錢買到主權？"},{"pid":"6377b34ddad0488452d61cddc1161b39156e2ffc","tid":1298478,"uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:34:14.000Z","msg":"本人是第一個提倡建人工